'''艾力克斯·寇茲曼'''（{{lang-en|Alex Kurtzman}}，{{bd|1973年|9月7日}}）是一位美國男編劇、監製和導演。

== 早期生活 ==
寇茲曼出生於[[加利福尼亞州|加利福尼亞州]]的[[洛杉磯|洛杉磯]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://stars.ign.com/objects/910/910973_biography.html|title=Alex Kurtzman Biography|work=[[IGN.com|IGN.com]]|accessdate=2012-08-16|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120106163910/http://stars.ign.com/objects/910/910973_biography.html|archivedate=2012-01-06}}</ref>，在那認識了他高中的朋友和長期合作者[[羅柏托·奧契|羅柏托·奧契]]。寇茲曼畢業於[[衛斯理大學|衛斯理大學]]<ref>{{cite web|last=Itzkoff|first=Dave|title=Character-Driven Films (but Keep the Kaboom)|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2007/06/24/movies/24dave.html?pagewanted=all&_r=0|publisher=New York Times|access-date=2016-02-18|archive-date=2019-10-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191019201048/https://www.nytimes.com/2007/06/24/movies/24dave.html?pagewanted=all&_r=0|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

